➜湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：在校园里扶正影子
http://www.sohu.com/a/419684868_100115135	40602
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200920/a99486c9209143fcb9ee2c964d6a8f62.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>在校园里扶正影子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣（武汉）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">忙碌在青春日子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在校园围墙里，杨柳依依</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那脆嫩的枝条</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">易动敏感神经，易飞莫名的烦恼柳絮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">光天里迷茫，寂寞如雪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拧不起忧郁的字迹</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在泛黄的日记里雁落孤影</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能烘干潮湿心的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是甘当一支案前流汗滴泪的蜡烛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">理当直立精神</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在阳光下举旗昂扬，十八的姑娘</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">扶正一群叽叽喳喳的少年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不让他们在风中倾斜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>写于2020年9月19日晚九点</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200920/dbc97ad8208a42d887601617d7a27d28.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
