➜广东诗人欧大象：咏秋月（外二首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/419686267_100115135	41166
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200920/1fae06c4a41540b3aa6d627db0ecfa42.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>咏秋月</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/欧大象</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">月满中天晖满湾，情人河畔乐开颜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">金风飒飒藏箫鼓，一曲南音醉碧山。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong>庚子秋</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200920/046f696d61d94d18ae1bba7a94c640be.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>行香子.吟秋月</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/欧大象</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">几缕浮烟，飘过中天。鸟啼林、声扰秋蝉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">浩茫星际，卿月悠然。或云中藏，风中笑，雨中眠。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">桂香醉夜，蟾宫邀会。共嫦娥、踏舞盘旋。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
